translation[10]{c,v,t}:
  28,85,"Inene(wenaMuhammad),loWoWakunikai’Kur’ân,Ukuyalela ukuba wenze ngokwemithetho yayo okuyishumayela, Yena Uya kukubuyisela kwindawo yakho yokubuyela9. Yithi: “INkosi yam yiYo Eyaziyo ukuba ngubani na okwisiKhokelo ingubani na osekulahlekeni okucacileyo"
  28,86,"Kananjalo wena wawungayilindelanga into yokuba kungaze kuthunyelwe iNcwadi kuwe, kodwa (oko kwenzekile ngenxa) yobabalo oluvela eNkosini yakho. Ngoko ke ungaze ube ngumxhasi wabangakholwayo"
  28,87,Ungaze kananjalo ubavumele bakuwexule kwiiVesi zika- Allâh emveni kokuba sele zityhiliwe kuwe. Kananjalo memela abantu eNkosini yakho. Ungaze ube ngomnye wabo bayamanisa abanye kuAllâh
  28,88,"Kananjalo uze ungaMnquli uAllâh ngokuMdibanisa nomnye uthixo. Akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe. Yonke into iza kutshabalala ngaphandle koBuso baKhe. OkwaKhe kukugweba, yaye kukuYe apho niza kubuyela khona"
  29,1,Alif-Lâm-Mîm
  29,2,"Ingaba abantu (aba) bacinga ukuba baza kuyekwa na kuba besithi: “Siyakholwa”, bangavavanywa"
  29,3,"Kodwa Sabavavanya abo bangaphambili kunabo, kwaye uAllâh Uza kwenza bacace abo banyanisekileyo, Abenze bacace nabo bangamaxoki"
  29,4,Makube mhlawumbi abo benza izenzo zokungcola bacinga ukuba bangaphuncula kuThi? Ingcolile (indlela) abagweba ngayo
  29,5,"Nabani na onethemba lokudibana noAllâh inene ixesha (elibekwe) nguAllâh liyeza. Yaye Yena nguSokuva, uSolwazi"
  29,6,"Ke kaloku lowo uzabalazayo, uzabalazela kuphela ukusindisa isiqu sakhe. Inene uAllâh Akadingi nto emaphakadeni"